title: Rolls-Royce jumps 6% after aerospace giant boosts profit outlook, plans up to $12 billion share buyback
summary_full: Rolls-Royce sees profits of over £4 billion this year as the engine and power systems maker banks on another year of robust growth.
summary_public: Rolls-Royce sees profits of over £4 billion this year as the engine and power systems maker banks on another year of robust growth.
